{"tid":98510,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"拜年真係好無聊","createTime":"2017-01-28T12:47:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-28T13:01:58.000Z","uid":57548,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6cf866d6053affc76aed23bcf7c656b34932f5ac","tid":98510,"uid":57548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T12:47:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 新年對我黎講只係放假，唔洗番學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n拜年又無聊，又要問長問短<br />\n係朋友面前好多野講 <br />\n對住成班親戚完全無心機同佢地講野<br />\n個個都叫錢開眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無人有同感<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"558f5e16e8c73a9ab21351b07662456fc371b49a","tid":98510,"uid":57548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T12:49:51.000Z","msg":"見錢開眼 先岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c89a74dcf055d451d98629c98c5e72f373a6823a","tid":98510,"uid":57062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T12:51:10.000Z","msg":"拜年真係好無聊"},{"pid":"f4dcee15305d211a3821ea3e5b6d35d07203dcb6","tid":98510,"uid":57548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T12:53:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>拜年真係好無聊</blockquote><br />\n諗起聽日仲要去，就想一直訓教<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d4860a9345741841cb82b140cfe1efc47675367","tid":98510,"uid":78769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T12:56:58.000Z","msg":"辛苦晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申:老豆唔洗我地去同佢果邊d人拜年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba716093c6acab299f907cf471da0c03a35fab0f","tid":98510,"uid":41353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T12:58:24.000Z","msg":"同意，班友一年見一次，我連佢叫咩名都唔知"},{"pid":"114c0fa79915ccdfa83c365d4f31c092358e3183","tid":98510,"uid":57548,"like